rows.label: qst102703_msg0001
rows.name:
I don't recognize you.
What do you need?

rows.label: qst102703_msg0003
rows.name:
She headed to Dokht's Spring,
saying she was looking for
ingredients for a new medicine.

rows.label: qst102703_msg0004
rows.name:
Going to a place like that
with only a single mercenary...
What a reckless doctor...

rows.label: qst102703_msg0101
rows.name:
Dokht's Spring is past the Plains
of Evening Calm, on the way to
the Wall of the Holy Gate.

rows.label: qst102703_msg0102
rows.name:
As its name implies, it is
a dangerous place surrounded
by a poisonous swamp.

rows.label: qst102703_msg0201
rows.name: Were you able to meet the doctor?

rows.label: qst102703_msg0202
rows.name: She's a strange one, but she's skilled.

rows.label: qst102703_msg0203
rows.name:
When she was assigned as a military
doctor, I saw her treat patients
with unerring accuracy.
